---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.endsWith("/")
  ? import.meta.env.BASE_URL
  : `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/`;
---

<section
  id="problema"
  class="bg-white px-5 py-12 md:px-8 md:py-20"
  aria-label="El problema que resolvemos"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4">
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-16"
    >
      <div class="problema-video-wrap scroll-reveal">
        <video
          class="problema-video"
          autoplay
          loop
          muted
          playsinline
          preload="metadata"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <source src={`${base}videos/bloque2.mp4`} type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </div>

      <div class="problema-content">
        <p class="section-label scroll-reveal">El problema</p>

        <h2
          class="gsap-split-title font-display mt-3 text-3xl leading-tight font-light text-[#0A0A0A] md:text-4xl"
        >
          ¿Sientes tu piel opaca, congestionada o sin vida?
        </h2>

        <p class="problema-paragraph scroll-reveal mt-5">
          La contaminación, el maquillaje y la grasa acumulada hacen que la
          piel pierda frescura y luminosidad.
        </p>

        <div class="problema-pills scroll-reveal mt-6" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="problema-pill">Piel opaca</span>
          <span class="problema-pill">Poros congestionados</span>
          <span class="problema-pill">Sin luminosidad</span>
        </div>

        <blockquote class="problema-quote scroll-reveal">
          Muchas veces tu piel no necesita maquillaje… necesita cuidado.
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problema-video-wrap {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 9 / 16;
    max-height: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background-color: #f3f4f6;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.06);
  }

  .problema-video {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  .problema-paragraph {
    font-family: "Poppins", system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .problema-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .problema-pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background-color: #fef3c7;
    color: #92400e;
    font-family: "Poppins", system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .problema-quote {
    margin-top: 32px;
    padding-left: 20px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--green-deep, #7ebc83);
    font-family: "Poppins", system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #0a0a0a;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .problema-video-wrap {
      max-height: 480px;
      max-width: 320px;
    }

    .problema-quote {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
